Mail/Summary version 0.01
=========================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Mail::Box::Manager
  Lingua::EN::Summarize

